CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1958, pg. B7, reads: "Charles F. Hall, of 437 North Graham St., Pittsburgh, chats with honor graduate Francis Ray Hewitt, of Springfield Vt., shortly before they received Bachelor of Fine Arts Degrees at Tech"
TitMainTitle: Men wearing dark caps and gowns, including Charles F. Hall and Francis Ray Hewitt, recipients of Bachelor of Fine Arts Degrees, at Carnegie Institute of Technology [Carnegie Mellon University] graduation
